txt.en: Torthol is in the Harper's Court in Dol Amroth.\n\nYou should return the sheet music to Torthol.
'Thank you, thank you! Now I can practice once more. The concert must go on!'

'Help, help! My music, my composition -- the pages have gone everywhere!

'I was practicing for a concert, and the wind took my sheets. Curse these stiff legs! I cannot catch them, for the wind whips them about too quick.

'Without my music, there can be no concert... I will be ruined!'
Torthol, a master musician, lost his sheet music while practicing for a concert, and his stiff legs will not allow him to catch the papers in time.
Return the sheet music to Torthol
Torthol's sheet music is floating around the Court.\n\nYou should pick up Torthol's sheet music.
